        </div>


<p>Returns a set of the elements in <code class="inline">List</code>.</p><h2 id="from_list/1-examples" class="section-heading"><a href="#from_list/1-examples" class="hover-link"><i class="ri-link-m" aria-hidden="true"></i></a><span class="text">Examples</span></h2><pre><code class="makeup erlang" translate="no"><span class="gp unselectable">1&gt; </span><span class="n">S</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nc">sets</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="nf">from_list</span><span class="p" data-group-id="2881760082-1">(</span><span class="p" data-group-id="2881760082-2">[</span><span class="ss">a</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="ss">b</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="ss">c</span><span class="p" data-group-id="2881760082-2">]</span><span class="p" data-group-id="2881760082-1">)</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="w">
