<p>Returns a set of the elements in <code class="inline">List</code> of the given version.</p><h2 id="from_list/2-examples" class="section-heading"><a href="#from_list/2-examples" class="hover-link"><i class="ri-link-m" aria-hidden="true"></i></a><span class="text">Examples</span></h2><pre><code class="makeup erlang" translate="no"><span class="gp unselectable">1&gt; </span><span class="n">S</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nc">sets</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="nf">from_list</span><span class="p" data-group-id="8678768285-1">(</span><span class="p" data-group-id="8678768285-2">[</span><span class="ss">a</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="ss">b</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="ss">c</span><span class="p" data-group-id="8678768285-2">]</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p" data-group-id="8678768285-3">[</span><span class="p" data-group-id="8678768285-4">{</span><span class="ss">version</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p" data-group-id="8678768285-4">}</span><span class="p" data-group-id="8678768285-3">]</span><span class="p" data-group-id="8678768285-1">)</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="w">
