  <section class="docstring">



<p>Returns <code class="inline">true</code> if <code class="inline">Set</code> is an empty set; otherwise, returns <code class="inline">false</code>.</p><h2 id="is_empty/1-examples" class="section-heading"><a href="#is_empty/1-examples" class="hover-link"><i class="ri-link-m" aria-hidden="true"></i></a><span class="text">Examples</span></h2><pre><code class="makeup erlang" translate="no"><span class="gp unselectable">1&gt; </span><span class="nc">sets</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="nf">is_empty</span><span class="p" data-group-id="2433920952-1">(</span><span class="nc">sets</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="nf">new</span><span class="p" data-group-id="2433920952-2">(</span><span class="p" data-group-id="2433920952-2">)</span><span class="p" data-group-id="2433920952-1">)</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="w">
</span><span class="ss">true</span><span class="w">
</span><span class="gp unselectable">2&gt; </span><span class="nc">sets</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="nf">is_empty</span><span class="p" data-group-id="2433920952-3">(</span><span class="nc">sets</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="nf">from_list</span><span class="p" data-group-id="2433920952-4">(</span><span class="p" data-group-id="2433920952-5">[</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p" data-group-id="2433920952-5">]</span><span class="p" data-group-id="2433920952-4">)</span><span class="p" data-group-id="2433920952-3">)</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="w">
