that are not elements in <code class="inline">Set2</code>.</p><h2 id="subtract/2-examples" class="section-heading"><a href="#subtract/2-examples" class="hover-link"><i class="ri-link-m" aria-hidden="true"></i></a><span class="text">Examples</span></h2><pre><code class="makeup erlang" translate="no"><span class="gp unselectable">1&gt; </span><span class="n">S0</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nc">sets</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="nf">from_list</span><span class="p" data-group-id="3462941677-1">(</span><span class="p" data-group-id="3462941677-2">[</span><span class="ss">a</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="ss">b</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="ss">c</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="ss">d</span><span class="p" data-group-id="3462941677-2">]</span><span class="p" data-group-id="3462941677-1">)</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="w">
