        </div>


<p>Returns the elements of <code class="inline">Set</code> as a list.</p><p>The order of the returned elements is undefined.</p><h2 id="to_list/1-examples" class="section-heading"><a href="#to_list/1-examples" class="hover-link"><i class="ri-link-m" aria-hidden="true"></i></a><span class="text">Examples</span></h2><pre><code class="makeup erlang" translate="no"><span class="gp unselectable">1&gt; </span><span class="n">S</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nc">sets</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="nf">from_list</span><span class="p" data-group-id="3472930507-1">(</span><span class="p" data-group-id="3472930507-2">[</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="mi">3</span><span class="p" data-group-id="3472930507-2">]</span><span class="p" data-group-id="3472930507-1">)</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="w">
</span><span class="gp unselectable">2&gt; </span><span class="nc">lists</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="nf">sort</span><span class="p" data-group-id="3472930507-3">(</span><span class="nc">sets</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="nf">to_list</span><span class="p" data-group-id="3472930507-4">(</span><span class="n">S</span><span class="p" data-group-id="3472930507-4">)</span><span class="p" data-group-id="3472930507-3">)</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="w">
</span><span class="p" data-group-id="3472930507-5">[</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="mi">3</span><span class="p" data-group-id="3472930507-5">]</span></code></pre>
